org.extremecomponents.table.bean
Class TableDefaults

java.lang.Object
  org.extremecomponents.table.bean.TableDefaults
final class TableDefaults
extends Object

Pull the complicated values for the TableTag. Because the default values could be coming from the properties or resource bundle this class will abstract that out.

Author:
Jeff Johnston
